---
title: Аутентификация (auth.py)
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Пользователь
    participant A as auth.py
    participant M as models.py
    participant T as templates/
    participant C as config.py

    U->>A: GET /login
    A->>T: render_template(login.html)
    T-->>U: Форма входа

    U->>A: POST /login<br/>(username, password)
    A->>M: get_user_by_username()
    M-->>A: User объект
    A->>A: check_password()
    A->>A: login_user()
    A-->>U: redirect /personal

    U->>A: GET /register
    A->>C: allow_registration?
    C-->>A: True/False
    alt Registration allowed
        A->>T: render_template(register.html)
        T-->>U: Форма регистрации
    else Registration blocked
        A-->>U: redirect /login + flash
    end

    U->>A: POST /register
    A->>M: get_user_count()
    M-->>A: count
    A->>M: create_user()
    M-->>A: User объект
    A-->>U: redirect /login + flash
